# 9ca3cc219313428f9b87b1c8c7047a1a
msgid "Relations are also very useful for creating, labeling and editing large linestrings; for example, bus routes, hiking trails, bicycle paths, etc. These differ from multipolygons because they are relations with members, as supposed to complex areas. A linestring could simply be one line with multiple members, these can be tagged as such. Additional features, such as bus stops represented by separate nodes can also be tagged as relation members."
msgstr ""

