msgid "Select all of the highways or ways that the bus takes. If you would only like to select certain parts of the way, then, sadly, you must divide the way into the section you would like to select. This creates more work, but you can easily do it with the :guilabel:`Split Way`tool. Once some or all of the ways are selected, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the :guilabel:`Relation` panel. The relation editing dialog will pop up."
